---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About {SITE.labName}</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE.labName} is dedicated to advancing research in sustainable building design and technology. 
        We leverage data-driven approaches and innovative methodologies to create solutions that benefit 
        both the environment and society.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Our team consists of passionate researchers, engineers, and students working across multiple 
        disciplines. We collaborate with leading institutions and industry partners to translate cutting-edge 
        research into practical applications.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Research Focus</h2>
      <p>
        We focus on several key research areas:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Sustainable Building Design:</strong> Developing eco-friendly construction methodologies and materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Energy Efficiency:</strong> Creating solutions to minimize energy consumption in buildings.</li>
        <li><strong>Smart Technologies:</strong> Integrating IoT and AI for intelligent building management.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Impact:</strong> Assessing and reducing the carbon footprint of construction projects.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> We push boundaries and explore new frontiers in sustainable technology.</li>
        <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> We work with partners worldwide to amplify our impact.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We share our findings openly and contribute to the scientific community.</li>
        <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Environmental responsibility guides all our decisions.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Interested in learning more about our work or potential collaborations? 
        <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Contact us</a> to get in touch with our team.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
